title: Mukhtar Ahmed Malik wins NA-82 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) Mukhtar Ahmed Malik has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-82 Sargodha-I Sahib-I by securing 1,08,714 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarian(PPPP) candidate Nadeem Afzal Gondal, who bagged 87,349 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 52.09 percent.
